  "body_preview": "Hi Natália, Thanks again for reaching out about your wedding.\nBased on the details I have so far, here are a few ballpark options from Comeketo Catering.\nI used our Comeketo food calculator as the sta",
  "body_text": "Hi Natália,\n\nThanks again for reaching out about your wedding.\nBased on the details I have so far, here are a few ballpark options from Comeketo Catering.\nI used our Comeketo food calculator as the starting point so these numbers stay grounded in the same pricing logic we use internally.\nYou can also take a look here: Comeketo Catering Interactive Menu and Price Calculator\nhttps://rawdre.github.io/comeketo-menu-landing/#packages\n\nThese are ballpark numbers so I can point you in the right direction without leading you the wrong way before we lock in your final guest count, menu, and service details.\n\nFull Churrasco\nA balanced full-service spread with our core Brazilian barbecue favorites.\nBase food price: $17.99 per person\n\nFull Churrasco (100 guests)\nFood: $17.99 x 100 = $1799.00\nAppetizers: $0.00 x 100 = $0.00\nMA Tax (7%): $125.93\nService, Fuel & Admin (24%): $431.76\nService Charge (over 50 guests at $3/pp): $300.00\nBallpark Total: ~$2656.69\n\nDeluxe Churrasco\nA stronger step up if you want a fuller wedding spread with more room to impress guests.\nBase food price: $20.99 per person\n\nDeluxe Churrasco (100 guests)\nFood: $20.99 x 100 = $2099.00\nAppetizers: $0.00 x 100 = $0.00\nMA Tax (7%): $146.93\nService, Fuel & Admin (24%): $503.76\nService Charge (over 50 guests at $3/pp): $300.00\nBallpark Total: ~$3049.69\n\nFor the meats, our default steak is Top Sirloin and our default chicken is Chicken Wrapped in Bacon.\nComplimentary cookies are included.\n\nWhich option feels closer to what you want for the event?\nIf it helps, we could also jump on a quick call at 10:00 AM, 11:00 AM, or 1:00 PM.\nOnce you tell me the guest count you expect to land on and which direction feels right, I can tighten this ballpark into the right next version for you.\n\n-----\nRegards,\nAndre Raw\n​​Catering Event Coordinator\n📲 C: (978) 235-3791\n📲 W: (978) 381-1212\nFacebook | Instagram | Website",
